==Chinese==
{{zh-forms|t2=怱|alt=悤-original form,忩,匇}}

===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
The original form is {{zh-l|悤}}, reinterpreted as a {{Han compound|囪|心|c1=p|c2=s|ls=psc|nocap=y}}.

The bottom left part of top component {{zh-l|*囪}} was omitted, arriving at the variant {{zh-l|*怱}}. Later, the semantic component {{zh-l|心}} was also omitted, arriving at 匆.

Unrelated to {{zh-l|*勿}}.

